    bf:tableOfContents [ a bf:TableOfContents ;
            rdfs:label "Innehåll: CD 1: Hold what you've got ; Be your own judge ; I let her get away ; I wanna be free ; Say thank you / Joe Tex -- I've got a thing going on ; I gotta sit down and cry ; Get down with it ; Half a mind ; Just be yourself / Bobby Marhan -- Somebody will ; I refuse to give up / Clarence Reid -- Only your love ; Chills and fever / Paul Kelly -- I want to (do everything for you) ; A sweet woman like you ; The love you save (may be your own) / Joe Tex -- Can't help it ; Since I found you / Paul Kelly -- You really fooled me / Chris Harris and the Soul Agents -- Gimme a try / Clarence Reid -- It comes and it goes / Len Wade -- You can't tie me down ; All I have to do / Little Archie -- I just want what belongs to me ; Sad sack / Bobby Marchan." ],
        [ a bf:TableOfContents ;
            rdfs:label "CD 2: Skinny legs and all / Joe Tex -- Don't let the sun shine on me / The Dialtones -- Hummin' a heartache ; This time ; THat's when I guessed / Clarence \"Frogman\" Henry -- I need you ; I am a carpet / Little Archie -- Dr. Funky ; Tell 'em I am who I am / Chris Harris -- Call another doctor (on the case) ; We're gonna make it / Paul Kelly -- Throw the switch ; I know where I've been / Frederick Knight -- Footprints on my mind ; I'll be your fool once more ; You oughta be here with me ; Get your thing together ; Just as hooked as I've ever been ; Love connection / Annette Snell -- Can you dig it? ; Learning to forget you / King Floyd -- Dirt ; Jesse Joe (you got to go) / Jean Knight -- Ain't nothin' wrong with Whitey / Bobby Marchan -- I gotcha / Joe Tex." ] ;
    bf:title [ a bf:Title ;
            rdfs:label "The Dial Records southern soul story." ;
            bflc:nonSortNum "4" ;
            bf:mainTitle "The Dial Records southern soul story." ] .

